content: Create a note,  a note can be related to an event or template. Relating a note to a template will automatically populate a note with the text in the template.
Text block can be added by clicking the + icon on the text editor. The text block selector can also be opened with the tab key.
A summary can be generated by clicking the refresh button. A summary is only generated for ''Question', 'Positive' or 'Negative' text blocks.
